Le Monde claims transcriptions of the calls showed Sarkozy and his lawyer were being fed information about internal judicial deliberations by a senior prosecutor at the appeals court described as a 'veteran supporter' of the political right.

The newspaper reports that Sarkozy tried to reward the prosecutor with an official post in Monaco.

Sarkozy's lawyer Thierry Herzog, said the revelations amounted to a 'monstrous' violation of his client's legal rights.

