Mr Herzog, said his client 'is probably still being tapped' and denounced what he described as a politically motivated plot against him.

He told AFP news agency: 'There was no attempt to pervert the course of justice and in due course this monstrous violation will be shown to have been a political affair.'

Sarkozy is said to have become aware that his phone was being tapped and that both he and Mr Herzog obtained second mobile phones which they used to communicate with each other.

